Example::

    cp -a tpl/ turnkey-rails-13.0
    cd turnkey-rails-13.0

    # add hotpatch version to the changelog (1 -> 2)
    vim $apps/rails/changelog
    cp $apps/rails/changelog debian/changelog

    head --lines 6 changelog 
    turnkey-rails-13.0 (2) turnkey; urgency=low

      * Regenerate Rails 4 hardwired secret in /var/www/railsapp

       -- Liraz Siri <alon@turnkeylinux.org>  Fri, 20 Jun 2014 11:22:43
       +0300

    sed -i 's/CODENAME/turnkey-rails-13.0/' control
